HEADWORD: Predetermination
<hw>Pre`de*ter`mi*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>pr⟦eacute⟧d⟦eacute⟧termination</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of
